-- Baird Says Canada Suspends Diplomatic Relations With Iran
-- B y   A n d r e w   M a y e d a
-- 2012-09-07T13:43:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-07/baird-says-canada-suspends-diplomatic-relations-with-iran.html
Canadian Foreign Affairs Minister
 John Baird  said his country is suspending diplomatic relations
with Iran and closing its embassy in Tehran.  Baird made the comments to reporters in Vladivostok, Russia
where he is attending an Asia-Pacific Economic Cooperation
summit.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrew Mayeda in Ottawa at 
 amayeda@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
